Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三次…世界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭的結果是 到2036年時全世界已經有57億人喪生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而戰爭的契機就是…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是機器人吧？會變形什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是時間機器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是叔叔 果然認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就好說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從α世界線來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這三週之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數次 無數次的改變世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜犧牲了紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才到達了這個β世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這一切成為徒勞…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像之前在廣播館被刺殺的科學家就叫這個名字哎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部倫太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說為了回避世界大戰所需要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拯救在2010年7月28日死去的牧瀬紅莉栖呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況我也不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我接到的任務只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拯救牧瀬紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:43.59,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(572,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且到達不受世界線收束範圍影響的唯一的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:46.32,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(685,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往命運石之門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:22.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(690,660)}境界面上的命運石之門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.46,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運石之門？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設立這個計劃的 是未來的叔叔和父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現階段一切都只是推測
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你們兩個的理論是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.78,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(665,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不存在命運石之門這條世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過即使如此我也還是要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上會有一個美好未來在等待的這個未知可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果叔叔願意和我一起去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就握住這隻手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…真由喜雖然對剛才這番話一頭霧水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫做紅莉栖小姐的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對岡倫來說是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那岡倫不是該努力一下才對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得第三次世界大戰之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和岡倫的妄想太接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以根本就沒別的人能依靠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對未來的57億人的性命沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快搭乘上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐兩個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 這可是出自我父親之手的最高傑作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手機留下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為可能會跟那邊叔叔帶的手機產生混淆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是時間機器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然我已經搭乘它去過1975年以及2000年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過運行狀態良好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 燃料要吃緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 它也能從過去跳向未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 因為是時間機器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和那時的世界線不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去的是7月28日12點前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為到達的地點是無法更改的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要是去的太早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會在廣播館引起騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會改變牧瀬紅莉栖的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次坐的話 估計會有很嚴重的重力反應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做好心理準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然會出現的東西 就像是時光碎片一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我胃液倒流了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不像話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免與這個時間點上的自己接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.68,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(859,660)}time paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那樣會引起嚴重的時間悖論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離她被刺還有多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有大約20分鐘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去設置時間機器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔去保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我叔叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日 我看到紅莉栖倒在血泊中的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和真由理一起參加了中鉢博士的見面會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後聽到了樓頂上發出的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說起來 真由理等一下會去7樓烏帕的轉蛋機那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是為了這個才叫我過來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個系列已經沒剩多少了 但真由喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百元硬幣用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 從裡面的樓梯回到8樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金屬的啊 金屬烏帕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很稀有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 超級稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖還…活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在哪裡見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在聽我說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…把妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:21.10,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 位於8樓大廳的中鉢博士見面會即將召開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:26.82,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 位於8樓大廳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間機器的基本構造如你們所見已經印在了發給大家的資料上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此我就只說明一下基礎理論
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就計劃書上來說 叔叔你應該要一直尾隨牧瀬紅莉栖才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 把她帶去外面也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能確認殺死她的兇手跟原因的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來很有可能還是一樣走向死亡的收束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟真由理那時一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博～士！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊？這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的時間機器理論是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克爾黑洞 世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是約翰·提托…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久 紅莉栖就將在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是在別的地方被刺了 然後再被搬到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這個可能性也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然接下來會在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在看的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間機器？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以紅莉栖在每次世界線改變後都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 混帳小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…希望您能看看這個 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是中鉢博士？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸時隔七年聯繫了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過要我來見面會對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就成為了契機喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:13.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 紅莉栖的父親是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整理了腦海中浮現的理論 覺得或許真的能製造出時間機器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽聽爸爸的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這篇論文能被承認的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逐出學會的爸爸也能捲土重來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是被逐出去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我看不慣他們 然後主動離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 只要爸爸你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為可以跟爸爸共同署名發表這篇論文
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為契機是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這篇論文會署上我一個人的名字然後發表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道爸爸你打算盜用我的論文嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為只有這種事您是絕對不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然敢說我盜用？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼就這麼優秀啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒道理孩子比父母還要優秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有妳 我就能一直保持優秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們事先商量好了 想要搞砸我的見面會對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…保護紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 爸爸 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別對我下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:13.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又明白些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感受 我的這份屈辱 我身處的地獄…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:38.64,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅…紅莉栖？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:13:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個笨蛋 真是和你們無比相襯的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 把你也牽扯進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是我父親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到爸爸的認同 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…還不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.60,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了 殺了 殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫 你那滿身的血是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這不是叔叔的血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我殺了…是我殺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…殺了紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我殺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔我知道你很痛苦 但還不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間機器還留有再一次回到過去的燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 就算再回去也一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:39.52,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(499,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正因為世界線收束範圍的收束 紅莉栖總會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 岡倫的手機…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 打開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs54\be2\fr-12\an1\move(204,578,191,545,600,1900)\t(600,1900,1,\fs70)}看電視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看電視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中鉢博士搭乘的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fr27\pos(653,581)\c&HB5B4B1&}中鉢博士 逃亡俄羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然貨物艙起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像仍然勉強在逃亡目的地的俄羅斯著陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 真是得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠這個東西被金屬探測器發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以論文沒有被大火燒毀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是真由喜的金屬烏帕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還寫著真由喜的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎 但是為什麼在俄羅斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇論文就是一切的起因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此為契機 大國之間展開了激烈的時間機器開發競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只要能統帥時間 就等於統帥了全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 最終發展成為了世界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事關57億人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救紅莉栖 然後改變世界線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟真由理那時是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論我怎麼掙扎 結果都不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖還是會死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是一次失敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道我已經失敗過幾次…幾十次了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時間之環究竟有多麼不講情理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有究竟會準備好多麼殘酷的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫不是那種會半途而廢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫絕對不是那種輕言放棄的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連真由喜無法跟奶奶說再見的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫也從未放棄 每天都會跟去墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真由喜才跟奶奶告別了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真由喜才變得這麼有精神喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不能放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日那天 應該有收到一封影音郵件才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話應該可以看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是「拯救牧瀬紅莉栖已經失敗過一次」的現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 瞞著沒告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要經歷過一次失敗其實也在計劃之內
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓叔叔看到這段影像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是初次見面吧 15年前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岡倫啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然已經打開了這封郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味著你在拯救紅莉栖這事上已經失敗過一次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過正是這份痛苦 給予了我執著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能把它當做是「未曾發生過的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說 這是相當於「事前準備」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來終於可以進入計劃的正題了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:24.06,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(824,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救牧瀬紅莉栖 並且進入命運石之門的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是把中鉢博士帶到俄羅斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於時間機器的論文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個世界上抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個 就是拯救牧瀬紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真能做到這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 想要回避牧瀬紅莉栖的死亡並且改變過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:48.08,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(461,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點由於世界線收束範圍的收束而成為了不可能的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就明說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救紅莉栖是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是方法有誤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我仔細聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能改變既定的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓一開始你自己見到的事情變成「未曾發生過的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是變成「未曾發生過」的話 就會造成過去改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓一切都付諸東流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起你在α世界線所經歷的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有短短三個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你應該還記得跟紅莉栖一同度過的時間才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟紅莉栖一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救真由理而犧牲了許多回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷掙扎的這份經歷 應該還存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓你那三個星期的世界線漂流白費
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕對不能把它當做「未曾發生過的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為你到達過無數條世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以渴望拯救紅莉栖的你才存在於那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把一切都奉獻給時間機器開發的我才存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在所身處的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為我們都渴望著拯救紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能到達的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 去欺騙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改變「紅莉栖已死」這個過去的情況下救活她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓過去的自己將還活著的紅莉栖「觀測」為已死的紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做的話 就不會引發過去改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話應該能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提 時間機器的型號是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C204型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首字母到底意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著我說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜（Cristina）…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:42.18,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(839,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外將目的地的世界線命名為命運石之門的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話應該也能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「並沒有什麼意義」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:59.61,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(625,660}Operation Skuld
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 對最終任務『掌管未來的女神』作戰的概要進行說明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改變既定過去的情況下改變結果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「渾身是血倒在地上的牧瀬紅莉栖」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及「目睹了這一切的岡部倫太郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改變這些既定過去的條件下改變結果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙最初的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:22.93,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是到達命運石之門的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,El Psy Congroo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個是15年後的岡倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音好低沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.05,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,660}Operation Skuld
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說『掌管未來的女神』？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說El Psy Congroo？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都33歲了我還在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是中二病全開嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就做到這一切給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.71,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說這就是命運石之門的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狂氣的科學狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰院凶真！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙世界這種小事 不值一提！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇喔 變回平時的那個岡倫了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 真由喜還是更喜歡這樣的岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我再說一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是狂氣的科學狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰院凶真！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界 是我的掌中之物！

Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:11.53,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去は離れて行き 未来は近づくの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:17.00,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,観測者はいつか 矛盾に気付く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:27.93,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神の創り出した世界は 完全なるもので 絶対の均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:34.81,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは折り重なる偶然 宇宙規模の奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:40.72,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守られてきた ゲート「規制」は終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.00,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:47.60,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「0」が過去で 「1」が未来 「今」は何処にもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:52.55,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背く事の出来ぬロジック
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.44,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:59.15,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並行する無数の線 選択は冒涜へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:04.49,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らの「存在」さえ疑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:10.94,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その目に映る景色は「収束」をする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:31.91,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二つの針が指す 時間の概念も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:37.46,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,観測者しだいで 歪みを見せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:48.46,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神に与えられた英知は 必ず「果て」がある 絶対の領域
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:54.96,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは愚かな故の偶然 招かれざる奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:23:00.89,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉ざされてきたゲート「規制」は終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:01.99,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.68,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光速へと手を伸ばした 想い出のパルスが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:12.71,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛び込む不可思議なロジック
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:13.57,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:19.20,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙がまだ隠し持った 秩序のない理論
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:24.35,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限と呼ばれた点と点が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:31.28,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正な力を借りて「再生」をする

Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:11.12,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去正在遠離 未來正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:16.59,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測者總有一天會發現矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:27.52,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神所創造出來的世界 是完美之物 擁有絕對的均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:34.40,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是重疊在一起的偶然 引發出宇宙規模的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:40.31,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被守護著的 Gate 終於結束「限制」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.59,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:47.19,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「0」是過去 「1」是未來 「現在」則不曾存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:52.14,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法違背的邏輯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.03,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:58.74,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並行排列的無數條線 選擇終將變為冒瀆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:04.08,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連我們的「存在」都會被質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:10.53,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼中映出的景色也終會「收束」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:31.50,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連兩枚指針所指出的時間概念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:37.05,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會向觀測者展現它的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:48.05,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由神所賦予的睿智 也終究會有「極限」 這是絕對的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:54.96,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是由於愚蠢的偶然 所招致而來的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:23:00.89,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被緊閉的Gate 終於結束「限制」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:01.99,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.68,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著光速伸出雙手 回憶的脈衝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:12.71,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛入不可思議的邏輯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:13.57,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:19.20,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙還未顯露出的 毫無秩序的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:24.35,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱作無限的點與點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:31.28,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助不正當的力量進行「重播」


